reviews.review_text: I was there with Berti Ami And Patty I was at that show as the Dead never played at 3rivers b4 they had the sound down 90 was a transation year Brent to Vince and Bruce they had a really cool sound the stadium sounded good Security was ok Pittsburg is a cool city This was a good break from RFK Giants or Jfk Stadiums  When Brent died I thought it was all over now but The boys pulled it together

never played their before? you might want to check out the show from 7/8/90.
it's also a View From the Vault DVD, you can actually see them play there too!
